WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.208
The sun sets turning the sky orange. A person carries a child, both silhouetted.

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:08.980
On a street,  a man holds bags as dust swirls around him.

00:00:09.005 --> 00:00:13.685
A child presses her face against a chainlink fence. She looks at the camera.

00:00:13.710 --> 00:00:17.498
A soccer ball rolls along dirt, then is kicked by a boy towards rubble.

00:00:17.523 --> 00:00:20.233
Silhouetted children watch the orange sunset.

00:00:20.356 --> 00:00:25.173
On a street, a boy and a girl stand. The boy holds a water cooler under his left arm.

00:00:25.198 --> 00:00:28.023
Elsewhere, three women sit behind baskets of fruit.

00:00:28.048 --> 00:00:31.073
On a filthy road, two people walk through garbage.

00:00:31.098 --> 00:00:37.739
In front of a dilapidated brick building, four boys play dominoes, using a piece of wood as a table.

00:00:37.790 --> 00:00:40.266
A malnourished dog looks for food.

00:00:40.291 --> 00:00:43.191
At night, a fire burns glowing bright orange.

00:00:43.216 --> 00:00:50.097
White text on a black background: January 12th, 2010. 4:53 p.m., Haiti.

00:00:50.122 --> 00:00:58.476
Traffic camera footage features a car approaching an intersection. It makes a right turn. The camera begins shaking violently.

00:00:58.523 --> 00:01:01.723
In another part of the city, a building collapses.

00:01:01.854 --> 00:01:06.531
Inside a building, a handheld camera shakes uncontrollably as people panic.

00:01:07.756 --> 00:01:17.006
Security footage features a man exiting a building. As he looks for somewhere to go,  there is an explosion and the man disappears from view, surrounded by dust and debris.

00:01:17.031 --> 00:01:18.856
Aerial footage of the desturction.

00:01:37.257 --> 00:01:40.740
In the aftermath, a building tilts, resting on its own debris.

00:01:40.765 --> 00:01:43.990
Elsewhere, signs and concrete have collpased on cars.

00:01:44.015 --> 00:01:47.607
A body wrapped in a sheet is placed in the bed of a truck.

00:01:47.632 --> 00:01:50.023
A man covered in blood sits on the ground.

00:01:50.048 --> 00:01:53.584
Another man writes on a brick wall in red: "We Need Help".

00:01:56.423 --> 00:01:59.356
A construction vehicle pulls a body out of debris.

00:01:59.381 --> 00:02:05.073
A person stuck between pieces of concrete reaches their arm through the space between slabs.

00:02:05.098 --> 00:02:08.240
On a sidewalk a motionless body is covered by a jacket.

00:02:08.265 --> 00:02:10.112
Another dead body lays amongst debris.

00:02:10.137 --> 00:02:13.706
A boy sits with a bloody bandage over his right eye.

00:02:13.731 --> 00:02:17.042
A woman lays on her back with a makeshift cast on her arm.

00:02:17.856 --> 00:02:21.423
A malnourished child is treated by gloved doctors.

00:02:23.156 --> 00:02:26.756
Text: As many as 300,000 Haitians injured.

00:02:27.273 --> 00:02:31.623
As many as 1.5 million Haitians left homeless.

00:02:31.648 --> 00:02:37.375
Estimates range from 85,000 to 300,000 Haitians killed.

00:02:38.344 --> 00:02:43.156
In a building, sparks shoot off the floor, as a man welds with a tool.

00:02:52.390 --> 00:02:54.990
Wilfrid holds a white prosthetic limb.

00:03:08.326 --> 00:03:12.576
A prosthetic foot is placed within an outline on a piece of paper.

00:03:12.601 --> 00:03:15.959
Blue text: Healing Haiti's Children.

00:03:23.656 --> 00:03:28.423
On a bustling street, crowds of people go about their days.

00:03:40.906 --> 00:03:43.090
In a river, two children bathe.

00:03:51.473 --> 00:03:54.740
In front of a destoryed building sits a pile of shoes.

00:04:03.170 --> 00:04:06.153
Chyron: Philippe R. Girard. Author.

00:04:15.832 --> 00:04:18.703
Chyron: Wilfrid Macena - Earthquake Survivor.

00:04:42.265 --> 00:04:45.481
Chyron: Mackenson Pierre - Earthquake Survivor.

00:05:19.584 --> 00:05:22.268
Chyron: Doctor Antonia Eyssallenne - Pediatrician.

00:05:39.073 --> 00:05:41.848
Three men peer into a destroyed building.

00:05:41.873 --> 00:05:47.173
Chyron: Fabiana Pierre. She sits with her 4-year-old daughter Anaika.

00:06:04.290 --> 00:06:08.306
Chyron: Leunese Gustave. Mother of 11-year-old Redondo.

00:06:25.862 --> 00:06:27.845
Chyron: Adam Finnieston. Project Medishare.

00:06:42.678 --> 00:06:45.928
Aerial footage shows a coastal Haitian city.

00:07:02.973 --> 00:07:06.073
Between two ramshackle houses, a boy carries jugs of water.

00:07:11.606 --> 00:07:16.073
Archival footage displays black and white photos on a wall.

00:07:25.323 --> 00:07:28.190
Papa Doc sits behind a desk wearing glasses.

00:07:48.700 --> 00:07:53.567
Historical footage of Papa Doc standing on a balcony and raising his arms in triumph.

00:08:13.378 --> 00:08:15.678
Men sprint alongside a motorcade.

00:08:33.790 --> 00:08:37.090
A police officer hits a boy and a woman with a piece of wood.

00:08:37.156 --> 00:08:39.134
Haitians run down the street in fear.

00:08:43.223 --> 00:08:48.840
Inside a house, news footage shows a woman and two children lying dead, blood pooling next to the woman's head.

00:09:05.218 --> 00:09:08.851
Archival footage of military personnel placing rifles on their shoulders.

00:09:33.096 --> 00:09:34.996
Baby Doc shakes hands with people.

00:09:48.529 --> 00:09:51.546
A man wears a t-shirt with Baby Doc's face on it.

00:10:26.318 --> 00:10:33.535
Footage from "Haiti: A Harvest of Hope" by Kevin Pina. The woman's words are subtitled: "They've done nothing." Chaos breaks out and people flee.

00:10:39.802 --> 00:10:44.018
In a street, a man lays dead as people look at him. Now, in the sky, a helicopter flies.

00:10:59.513 --> 00:11:06.930
A clip from "Power &amp; People - Haiti: Hope Among the Rubble" an All Jazeera Broadcast shows Rene Preval. Subtitles: "I don't like being late."

00:11:19.624 --> 00:11:22.574
In front of a maskehift tent, a woman holds her baby.

00:12:03.336 --> 00:12:07.452
A plane flies overhead and drops parchuted supplies to the ground.

00:12:07.652 --> 00:12:11.969
Chyron: First Lieutenant Cameron Kerr: U.S. Army.

00:12:25.522 --> 00:12:27.689
Chyron: Doctor Robert Gailey. Program Director.

00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:07.550
Chyron: Jason Miller. In-country Program Director.

00:13:07.575 --> 00:13:09.240
Now, inside a makeshift hospital.

00:13:24.186 --> 00:13:28.450
A doctor holds a young crying child who has an IV hooked up to them.

00:13:29.269 --> 00:13:30.819
Doctors perform surgery.

00:13:30.844 --> 00:13:33.602
A woman closes the doors to the hospital.

00:13:51.412 --> 00:13:53.430
A bandaged child is cared for.

00:13:53.517 --> 00:13:56.845
A man comforts a child with a large cast on her arm.

00:13:56.881 --> 00:13:59.330
Anaika looks on as her mother speaks.

00:14:18.884 --> 00:14:21.800
At a soccer field, Leunese stands alongside Redondo.

00:15:45.776 --> 00:15:49.426
Chyron: Jean Jacob Pierre - Father of Mackenson.

00:16:34.782 --> 00:16:40.315
In the hospital, doctors wearing masks and blue scrubs operate on a patient.

00:16:49.098 --> 00:16:51.982
A girl with an amputated right arm lays in a bed.

00:16:52.007 --> 00:16:55.998
A person with a normal left foot and an amputated right foot fidgets in bed.

00:17:09.593 --> 00:17:13.993
Outside, a boy with a bandage on his arm is carried by a group of people.

00:17:30.856 --> 00:17:32.923
Chyron: Dr. Marlon Bitar.

00:17:38.940 --> 00:17:42.040
Outside a man with a beard points at a canvas tent.

00:17:54.223 --> 00:17:55.973
Chyron: Dr. Enrique Ginzburg.

00:18:11.719 --> 00:18:13.353
An IV drip is hung.

00:18:29.890 --> 00:18:32.073
A doctor inserts rods into a patient's leg.

00:18:52.823 --> 00:18:56.139
In a bed, a baby with both legs in casts, sleeps.

00:19:06.923 --> 00:19:09.390
Chyron: Dr. Gerry Bitar.

00:19:20.769 --> 00:19:23.319
In the makeshift hospital, numerous patients lay in cots.

00:19:57.631 --> 00:19:59.747
Chyron: Dr. Michael J. Dodard.

00:20:21.325 --> 00:20:23.925
In a field, one-legged Anaika stands with crutches.

00:20:42.712 --> 00:20:47.745
A patient is loaded into a covered area. A woman has an IV hooked to her arm.

00:20:47.770 --> 00:20:51.328
A child's leg and foot are covered in white splotches.

00:20:58.778 --> 00:21:02.795
On the soccer field, Redondo walks with crutches.

00:21:40.826 --> 00:21:42.709
Rods stick out of a child's leg.

00:21:48.511 --> 00:21:50.768
A doctor comforts a female patient.

00:21:50.793 --> 00:21:54.476
A patient has a breathing mask removed from his face.

00:22:05.629 --> 00:22:09.463
In an operating room, doctors check monitors while performing surgery.

00:22:49.107 --> 00:22:51.557
A doctor puts a latex glove on.

00:23:18.260 --> 00:23:20.760
Now, Wilfrid sits next to his wife and holds his baby.

00:23:36.055 --> 00:23:40.205
Text: As many as 2,500 Haitians lost limbs.

00:23:41.690 --> 00:23:46.772
In front of a the severely damaged capitol building, a white car drives by.

00:24:01.800 --> 00:24:04.616
UN military personnel try to control a crowd.

00:24:13.350 --> 00:24:19.066
A helicopter drops packages from the sky. People run after, and fight over, the supplies.

00:24:35.678 --> 00:24:39.178
Chyron: Ambassador John Simon.

00:25:29.650 --> 00:25:32.000
Doctors carry an operating table.

00:26:17.056 --> 00:26:19.656
In a warehouse, a forklift transports boxes.

00:27:02.851 --> 00:27:05.601
A palette of supplies is loaded onto a cargo ship.

00:27:44.224 --> 00:27:47.157
Chyron: Barth A. Green, MD, FACS.

00:28:07.902 --> 00:28:11.218
A nurse walks through the Medishare courtyard.

00:28:29.335 --> 00:28:32.018
A palette of cargo is taken out of a truck.

00:29:02.682 --> 00:29:04.699
Two men look at a photo of a mother and daughter.

00:29:12.549 --> 00:29:14.882
Chyron: Davor Krchelich.

00:29:37.994 --> 00:29:41.610
On a busy street, a boy amputee uses crutches to walk.

00:29:57.355 --> 00:30:00.422
A girl lays in a hospital bed and holds a doctor's hand.

00:30:18.073 --> 00:30:20.940
Under a tent, a boy sits in a wheelchair.

00:30:20.965 --> 00:30:25.090
Chyron: Andrew Walther. Vice President, Communications. Knights of Columbus.

00:30:51.217 --> 00:30:54.284
In a hospital, a young person tests their new prosthetic.

00:31:08.200 --> 00:31:12.525
Chyron: Carl A. Anderson. Supreme Knight. The Knights of Columbus.

00:31:30.053 --> 00:31:34.670
In the lab, Adam measures the length of a prosthetic foot.

00:32:12.309 --> 00:32:15.259
Now, Davor holds a bioscanner and works at a computer.

00:32:37.056 --> 00:32:38.906
A prosthetic is molded by a machine.

00:32:46.156 --> 00:32:52.514
In a hospital, Adam meets with Anaika. He measures from her residual limb to the floor with a tape measurer.

00:32:52.539 --> 00:32:57.340
Adam fits the prosthetic casing to her limb, and Anaika wiggles it.

00:33:00.090 --> 00:33:03.756
Outside, Wilfrid sits on a bench with other Haitian men.

00:33:23.410 --> 00:33:26.760
On a dirt road, Wilfrid walks with his prosthetic leg.

00:33:44.946 --> 00:33:46.996
Wilfrid and his family share a happy moment.

00:34:41.669 --> 00:34:44.786
Through a night vision lens, a firefight ensues.

00:34:44.811 --> 00:34:47.786
In a desert, military troops endure combat.

00:35:01.456 --> 00:35:04.890
Troops carry a stretchered man to an aircraft.

00:35:26.797 --> 00:35:33.897
Text: More than 1,500 U.S. service men and women have lost a limb since September 11, 2001.

00:35:33.922 --> 00:35:36.830
Chyron: Sergeant Justin Masellas. U.S. Marine Corps.

00:35:45.356 --> 00:35:46.173
Matthew Castillo del Muro.

00:36:36.060 --> 00:36:42.476
On a silhouetted Haitian street, people move around as the sun sets and turns the sky orange.

00:36:56.865 --> 00:36:59.449
On a busy street, a car passes Wilfrid.

00:37:25.435 --> 00:37:27.535
A car drives a road along a forest.

00:37:27.560 --> 00:37:31.285
On a bustling dirt road, a truck navigates pedestrians.

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:02.030
Chyron: Fortilus Cedieu.

00:38:34.990 --> 00:38:37.786
Wilfrid helps an amputee fit into their prosthetic.

00:39:28.090 --> 00:39:32.390
The sun rises over mountains that surround a ramshackle town.

00:39:49.285 --> 00:39:51.151
A woman gets water from a pump.

00:41:15.251 --> 00:41:17.768
In Carl's office, a soccer ball is displayed.

00:41:38.523 --> 00:41:43.573
On a soccer field, Mackenson and Redondo, both on crutches, kick a soccer ball to one another.

00:42:25.960 --> 00:42:28.277
A man sets down a handful of crutches.

00:42:58.875 --> 00:43:03.693
On the field, numerous men on crutches play soccer as fans look on.

00:43:50.083 --> 00:43:52.867
A group of players in blue shirts celebrate.

00:43:59.117 --> 00:44:03.134
The team as well as their supporters pose for a photo.

00:44:05.767 --> 00:44:11.790
An airplane flies through a clear blue sky above the soccer field where the team practices.

00:44:30.307 --> 00:44:32.264
Chyron: Seth Stammler.

00:44:32.289 --> 00:44:34.841
A player wearing red loses his crutch. He picks it up.

00:44:45.074 --> 00:44:47.706
Text: Five months later.

00:44:50.756 --> 00:44:57.089
Two teams of amputee players walk in two lines side by side. One wears red. One wears blue.

00:45:23.386 --> 00:45:27.802
Players on both teams chase after the ball. A player in red kicks it.

00:45:55.620 --> 00:45:59.670
Later, the blue team lines up, then takes the field.

00:46:35.389 --> 00:46:39.122
The red team stretches in a circle arms extended to their sides.

00:46:50.990 --> 00:46:56.390
A player focuses on the ball in the air, then using his crutches for support, kicks it.

00:46:57.640 --> 00:47:00.540
Players from both teams chase after the ball.

00:47:00.565 --> 00:47:04.423
A player kicks the ball right at the camera and it cuts to black.

00:47:04.448 --> 00:47:07.806
A soccer ball with blue writing: Zaryen.

00:47:45.329 --> 00:47:48.612
A player in blue kicks the ball with the outside of his foot.

00:47:48.637 --> 00:47:52.862
Text: October 15, 2011. In a house, a man walks up stairs.

00:47:56.046 --> 00:48:00.162
Outside, players in matching white shirts, greet each other.

00:48:09.314 --> 00:48:11.547
The players get in the back of a truck.

00:48:22.880 --> 00:48:28.064
The truck pulls up at the aiport where other people in the same white shirts are waiting.

00:48:28.089 --> 00:48:32.898
The players unload the truck and walk under an awning toward the terminal.

00:48:36.048 --> 00:48:38.082
In the airport, players wait for their flight.

00:49:00.934 --> 00:49:09.869
Through a plane's window, the plane speeds along a tarmac and lifts off the ground. As the plane rises, a Haitian town and mountains become more apparent.

00:49:10.003 --> 00:49:13.736
Now, above the clouds, Haiti is barely visible below.

00:49:13.836 --> 00:49:17.103
On the plane, a player sleeps in an aisle seat.

00:49:44.897 --> 00:49:48.750
In Washington, D.C., the team walks through the terminal.

00:50:00.884 --> 00:50:02.184
On a bus, the team looks at sites.

00:50:07.159 --> 00:50:09.759
Outside the bus, a woman takes a photo.

00:50:25.575 --> 00:50:29.642
On the steps of the Capitol Building, the team sits and poses for a photo.

00:50:30.223 --> 00:50:33.256
On a field, an amputee on crutches kicks a soccer ball.

00:50:33.281 --> 00:50:36.505
Another amputee laces up his shoe.

00:50:36.530 --> 00:50:39.223
A soldier and Haitian kick a ball to each other.

00:50:39.248 --> 00:50:41.456
Chyron: Rear Admiral Alton L. Stocks.

00:50:53.951 --> 00:50:55.368
Chyron: William Parker.

00:51:26.093 --> 00:51:28.993
A solider dribbles around a cone.

00:51:54.971 --> 00:51:57.687
On a street, Team Zaryen exits a bus.

00:52:08.287 --> 00:52:10.554
Chyron: Colonel Paul Pasquina.

00:52:23.490 --> 00:52:27.190
On an indoor soccer field, the players stand around the midfield circle.

00:52:44.652 --> 00:52:47.335
Wilfrid shows soldiers how to use the crutches.

00:53:16.255 --> 00:53:19.488
A member of Team Zaryen receives a pass from a solider.

00:53:33.333 --> 00:53:36.049
Masellas falls, laughs, then stands up.

00:53:50.133 --> 00:53:54.749
Masellas scores a goal. A member of Team Zaryen celebrates and hugs Masellas.

00:54:24.593 --> 00:54:28.693
On the field, del Muro walks with his crutches. He stops and rests.

00:54:28.718 --> 00:54:33.827
Text: October 18 ,2011. On an outdoor soccer field, players warm up.

00:54:35.144 --> 00:54:42.810
Text: Team Zaryen vs. U.S. National Amputee Soccer Team. D.C. United Practice Facility, R.F.K. Stadium.

00:54:42.835 --> 00:54:45.310
A reporter speaks with Wilfrid.

00:55:06.887 --> 00:55:09.137
The teams pose for a photo together.

00:55:09.162 --> 00:55:13.304
At midfield, a ref holds a soccer ball, as teams take their sides.

00:55:14.154 --> 00:55:17.587
The game begins. Zaryen wears red. The U.S. wears white.

00:55:23.065 --> 00:55:26.615
The U.S. shoots the ball on net, but the goalkeeper saves it.

00:55:29.532 --> 00:55:35.465
A U.S. player dribbles down the field past Zaryen defenders. He cuts the ball back, then passes it to a teammate.

00:55:36.432 --> 00:55:40.015
A U.S. player passes the ball past the Zaryen defense to his teammate.

00:55:40.965 --> 00:55:43.382
The teammate shoots and scores.

00:55:45.799 --> 00:55:49.255
Two Zaryen players chase after the ball in the open field.

00:55:50.483 --> 00:55:54.650
A Zaryen player shoots but the ball is saved by the American goalie.

00:55:59.617 --> 00:56:04.183
An American players steals the ball from a Zaryen player. The Haitian falls to the ground.

00:56:04.967 --> 00:56:09.700
Later, the U.S. goalie attempts to get the ball but misses and tackles another Haitian player to the ground.

00:56:09.800 --> 00:56:12.467
Now, the Zaryen goalie helps an American up.

00:56:12.492 --> 00:56:15.356
Later, a Zaryen player shoots and again the shot is saved.

00:56:17.523 --> 00:56:22.223
Team America takes a free kick. The ball is headed into the back of the net for a goal.

00:56:26.123 --> 00:56:29.490
Now, moving slowly, the Zaryen players look defeated.

00:56:50.086 --> 00:56:53.519
As the second half gets underway, a Zaryen player kicks the ball

00:56:54.685 --> 00:57:03.968
A Zaryen defender blocks a shot. The U.S. player tracks the ball down and passes it his teammate. The Zaryen goalie readies himself. He blocks the U.S. player's shot attempt.

00:57:08.141 --> 00:57:12.974
A Zaryen player sprints down the field with the ball. He passes it to a teammate.

00:57:12.999 --> 00:57:15.141
His teammate kicks the ball toward the net.

00:57:17.476 --> 00:57:19.156
It gets past the goalie.

00:57:20.558 --> 00:57:25.084
Members of Team Zaryen throw their crutches in the air in celebration.

00:57:30.777 --> 00:57:34.360
After the game, the players from both teams meet and hug.

00:57:42.878 --> 00:57:44.561
Wilfrid signs autographs.

00:57:45.928 --> 00:57:48.678
Chyron: Dwayne De Rosario. D.C. United.

00:58:02.713 --> 00:58:05.829
Players and coaches from both teams pose for a photo.

00:58:14.825 --> 00:58:19.096
At a stadium, the D.C. United mascot waves a flag over its head.

00:58:21.597 --> 00:58:25.063
D.C. United wears black and plays against a team in red.

00:58:27.311 --> 00:58:30.061
In a locker room, Team Zaryen meets Coach Ben Olsen

00:59:11.968 --> 00:59:14.218
In the stands, fans cheer on their D.C. United.

00:59:55.539 --> 00:59:59.589
Chyron: Aprile Pritchet: Director of Community Relations. D.C. United.

01:00:06.603 --> 01:00:09.403
The members of Team Zaryen exit the field.

01:00:10.156 --> 01:00:15.022
A soccer ball rolls across a rocky, dirt field. A Haitian boy kicks it.

01:00:35.883 --> 01:00:37.384
An amputee girl kicks a ball.

01:00:58.128 --> 01:01:01.678
On a soccer field, Mackenson watches Redondo.

01:01:46.807 --> 01:01:49.741
A bustling Haitian street glows orange as the sun sets.

01:01:50.457 --> 01:01:53.107
At a stream, a woman washes clothes.

01:01:53.191 --> 01:01:56.091
On a very busy street, people navigate cars.

01:02:25.001 --> 01:02:29.018
On a plot of dirt, a boy joyfully throws a soccer ball into the air.

01:02:53.096 --> 01:02:56.462
Haitian amputees practice side step drills between cones.

01:03:25.657 --> 01:03:27.990
At a hospital, Antonia looks inside a crib.

01:03:38.635 --> 01:03:41.202
A split screen of both tents full of people.

01:04:06.313 --> 01:04:09.963
Outside, Fabiana carries Anaika up a set of stairs.

01:04:21.513 --> 01:04:23.513
Adam fits Anaika's prosthetic.

01:04:39.008 --> 01:04:42.458
Adam helps Anaika walk with her new prosthetic leg.

01:05:14.452 --> 01:05:18.786
Text: Mackenson sees Redondo with his prosthetic for the first time.

01:05:33.847 --> 01:05:39.580
Inside a building, Mackenson smiles as he watches Redondo walk with his prosthetic leg.

01:05:39.864 --> 01:05:41.880
Redondo looks at himself in a mirror.

01:05:45.156 --> 01:05:48.006
Redondo dances as Mackenson watches.

01:05:57.773 --> 01:05:59.133
Mackenson dances.

01:06:15.210 --> 01:06:20.693
Mackenson and Redondo shake hands, then Mackenson pulls the boy in for a hug.

01:06:22.493 --> 01:06:28.448
Chyron: Three years later. Inside the prosthetic factory, limbs are made by Haitians.

01:06:43.958 --> 01:06:45.638
A giant red gate opens.

01:07:53.234 --> 01:07:57.401
Inside a room, the Medishare teams sits at a table with Haitains.

01:08:56.023 --> 01:08:59.123
The Haitian flag blows in the wind as the sun sets.

